    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <i class="icon-relevant-to-the-topic"></i>
            <h3>Why Choose Us?</h3>
            <p>Experience the benefits of our free and volunteer-based therapy services provided by dedicated
                professionals.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <i class="icon-relevant-to-the-topic"></i>
            <h3>Choose a Psychologist</h3>
            <p>Select a professional who matches your criteria and makes you feel comfortable.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <i class="icon-relevant-to-the-topic"></i>
            <h3>Privacy</h3>
            <p>Get support without sharing your personal information. Share your application reason with your
                therapist, along with the trust you have in confidentiality.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <i class="icon-relevant-to-the-topic"></i>
            <h3>No Cost Involved</h3>
            <p>Access therapy services at no cost on our platform.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <i class="icon-relevant-to-the-topic"></i>
            <h3>Affordable for Everyone</h3>
            <p>Connect with a wide network of therapists who offer their services free of charge, catering to different
                budgets and needs.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
            <i class="icon-relevant-to-the-topic"></i>
            <h3>Start Therapy Immediately</h3>
            <p>Get support at any time of the day from anywhere with an internet connection to continue your therapy
                process according to your own schedule.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</div>
<!-- End of Info -->

